name: 50 Day Glo - DayGlo - Posters A3
description:
COLOUR:
A3 Day Glo posters are printed in Black

STOCK:
Our A3 Day Glo posters are printed on 100gsm silk Art Paper

DELIVERY:
We operate a 5 days a week, 24hrs a day. If your order is placed before 11am you will receive your flyers or leaflets 3 working days later. All our orders are delivered via businesspost courier. Full tracking details will be emailed to you once your order has been despatched.

ARTWORK:
We can accept most file types, our preferred format is PDF with all fonts embedded or convert all fonts to paths/outlines. We can accept JPEG, TIFF and EPS format.
We require 3mm bleed on each edge, this is integral to our production process. To avoid delays don't forget your bleed.
